{"title":"Android Note 1","date":"2018-12-04T06:00:55.000Z","slug":"androidDay1","comments":true,"categories":["Android Note"],"updated":"2018-12-04T06:04:58.959Z","content":"<p>Day 1:<br>follow <a href=\"https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/build-your-first-android-app-kotlin/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">build-your-first-android-app-kotlin</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Check-view-ID\"><a href=\"#Check-view-ID\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Check view ID\"></a>Check view ID</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">val showCountTextView = findViewById&lt;TextView&gt;(R.id.counter)</span><br><span class=\"line\">val buttonID: button = findViewById(R.id.button)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Interactive-with-button\"><a href=\"#Interactive-with-button\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Interactive with button\"></a>Interactive with button</h3><ul>\n<li><p>By listener:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">toast_button.setOnClickListener &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .......</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>By layout xml and function</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"A-simple-Kotlin-function\"><a href=\"#A-simple-Kotlin-function\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"A simple Kotlin function:\"></a>A simple Kotlin function:</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fun countMe (view: View) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ......</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>arguments: (variable name: variable type = default value)</li>\n<li><p>what is the variable type of “view: View”?</p>\n<p>  view: the objects in activity (like TextView, Button, …)<br>  due to we use “android: onClick=”xxx” “ in the layout xml files for buttons, we need this argument!</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Kotlin-string\"><a href=\"#Kotlin-string\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Kotlin string:\"></a>Kotlin string:</h3><ul>\n<li><p>concatenate:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">val a = &quot;Hello&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">val b = &quot;World&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">val c = &quot;$a $b&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">val c = a + b   // same as calling operator function a.plus(b)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">val sb = StringBuilder()</span><br><span class=\"line\">sb.append(a).append(b)</span><br><span class=\"line\">val c = sb.toString()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>string to Int (or other):</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><figcaption><span>count: Int </span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">### Second activity</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- add a new activity from</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">```main-&gt;java-&gt;com.xxx...-&gt;(right click)-&gt;New</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>check activity status from “AndroidManifest.xml”</li>\n<li><p>go to the new activity and send some info:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fun go_to_act2(view: View)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   val act2 = Intent(this, Main2Activity::class.java)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   act2.putExtra(Main2Activity.mainActNum, count.toString())</span><br><span class=\"line\">   startActivity(act2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>receive the info in the new activity:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>create a static object</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">companion object &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       const val mainActNum = &quot;wtf&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>receive from intent</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fun getMainActValue(view: View)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       val myIntent = intent</span><br><span class=\"line\">       val count = myIntent.getStringExtra(mainActNum)</span><br><span class=\"line\">       Second_view_text.text = count</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","link":"http://yoursite.com/post/androidDay1/"}